events.name: 巨大な魚影：漁師オルカ

parameters:
Fisherman Orca: Ever since that reckless noble arrived, the
lake has been acting strange. Those imperial people always
bring nothing but trouble to Wald!
Fisherman Orca: Did you happen to see the bulletin board?
Clea: Yes, please tell me the details of the request.

Fisherman Orca: There's a huge, ferocious fish that appears
in this lake. It eats anything and everything, so it's
become a lucrative business!

Fisherman Orca: Ever since that idiot noble showed up,
nothing but strange things have been happening!

Mage Relm: Could it be about Mr. Luid...? The special pearl-
making might be causing some influence, you know.

Fisherman Orca: I tried to request assistance from the Bulk
Gang, but those people are too heavily equipped. It feels
like the ship would sink.

Fisherman Orca: If it's me and four women, we should be able
to handle it. Please change into lightweight clothing and
then let me know.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
EV：VIPルームにクレア以外で入ろうとする

Fisherman Orca: I want to decide whether to depart with the
leader girl.
EV：VIPルームにクレアが水着以外の服装で入ろうとする

Fisherman Orca: Did you listen to what I said? I'm asking
you to wear lighter clothes, even if it's just a little.

Clea: I changed my equipment to be as light and water-
resistant as possible. How does it look?

Fisherman Orca: N-Nothing! Now, if you're ready, let's
depart.
Fisherman Orca: Everyone, please get on the boat.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Fisherman Orca: This is the usual reward... and an
additional reward.
Clea: Thank you very much, then.

Fisherman Orca: Artworks don't fade, that's why they're
artworks. If you can touch artworks, then money is not a
concern.

Fisherman Orca: I'm looking forward to receiving requests on
the bulletin board.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Fisherman Orca: You are the embodiment of my ideal, and I
pray to the goddess Deiree that I may have the chance to
touch you.

Fisherman Orca: I'm really grateful that I can fish in
peace!

events.name: トランパ

parameters:
Trap Master Trampa: I can assert that there is no way of
life better than completing work and drinking beer.
Thief Nora: I-I've checked the bulletin board!

Trap Master Trampa: Please don't raise your voice! There is
no greater humiliation for a trap master!
Clea: Can you tell me what I should do?

Trap Master Trampa: All the traps in the hunting grounds are
broken... It must have been the bears that caused the
damage!

Trap Master Trampa: There is no creature as dangerous as a
wounded bear with blood on its traps... I want you to defeat
it without fail.
Thief Nora: U-Understood! Leave it to us!

Trap Master Trampa: Hurry up! Once you're ready, head
towards that passage over there!

Trap Master Trampa: I apologize for the chaotic state of the
hunting grounds due to the destroyed traps, but I also ask
for your help in cleaning up while we subdue the bears.
Trap Master Trampa: What happened to the injured bear!?

Thief Nora: The bear was suffering quite a lot... Please
make sure to set up traps properly next time.
Thief Nora: S-Sorry for speaking out of turn!

Trap Master Trampa: As a trap master for several decades...
perhaps I became a bit arrogant somewhere along the way.

Trap Master Trampa: Thank you, young lady. It feels like
I've returned to my roots as a trap master.

Trap Master Trampa: This is my gratitude for your reward and
advice.
Thief Nora: T-Thank you very much!

Trap Master Trampa: Thanks for saving me! Let me treat you
to a beer someday.
